This is a skeleton that remodeled XPMSE.

// This is a skeleton that remodeled XPMS(12 Back Hip Daggers).

Body become leggy, other parts become small a little.


========<< install >>=========
Overwrite to an arbitrary skeleton.

========<< uninstall >>=========
Delete skeleton and return your skeleton.


========<< notice >>=========
I am not considering your Skyrim environment(motion,outfit etc)

I recommend installing it into the environment to which XPMSE(XPMS) is steady.

I cannot solve your problem.
